{"tid":2330282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"死無全偲 李偲嫣遺體須經病理科醫生解剖","createTime":"2020-12-18T01:16:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T06:42:58.000Z","uid":5655,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"68db98ee9861a815611e086f7eaf874b811fcad0","tid":2330282,"uid":5655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T01:16:11.000Z","msg":"盲撐梁振英的正義聯盟創辦人李偲嫣昨日猝死，博愛醫院證實其樣本對武漢肺炎測試呈陽性反應，終年56歲。因李初步確診感染武漢肺炎，目前死因不明，故須交往死因裁判官決定是否召開死因庭，相信遺體須經病理科醫生解剖，向死因庭交報告。李偲嫣遺體屬於《處理及處置屍體時所需的預防措施》下第2類，家人可在殯儀館內瞻仰遺容，為遺體裝身及化妝 ，不可以為遺體進行防腐。有殯儀業人士表示，有同業會協助處理此類遺體，但一般是將遺體由殮房直接運送到火葬場火化，將與遺體的接觸減到最少。"},{"pid":"47e36a72043459602e032111693bc1c46b078292","tid":2330282,"uid":31946,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T01:17:27.000Z","msg":"最後仲要變煙灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163366845202e8ad62ea13270282655d88852524","tid":2330282,"uid":195248,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T01:18:05.000Z","msg":"幫佢整返套水手裝壽衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c14aff569c7bc3cd12c2908e2c0baf3e0549bf","tid":2330282,"uid":40272,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T01:20:52.000Z","msg":"一開個頭係無腦既"},{"pid":"99a51c09b9a9a49289fe72455fb04d0653ef220b","tid":2330282,"uid":81214,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T01:22:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9JbfBvk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9JbfBvk.jpg&h=3f938762&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59fe2d945a490b100c6b1cf163f80c12345ffe9f","tid":2330282,"uid":11447,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T01:22:27.000Z","msg":"劏開發現個肺寫住made in china"},{"pid":"24940032ff162b0a874e70d9409bf1c67483a9ba","tid":2330282,"uid":283912,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"163366845202e8ad62ea13270282655d88852524","tid"